title: Olivia Culpo has found love in Tim Tebow
text:
Olivia Culpo has found love in Tim Tebow 
Entertainment Industry News.Net (ANI) : Saturday 3rd October, 2015 
Hollywood just got its new couple as Tim Tebow and Olivia Culpo are dating each other for over a month. 
According to sources, the 23-year-old actress, who had a hard time after her split with Nick Jonas, is dating the 28-year-old footballer, but they are trying to keep themselves out of public eyes, reports E! Online. 
The insider added that the former Miss USA is taking a chance and is getting to know the player and they love spending time with each other. 
Meanwhile, the football stud is really enjoying getting to know Culpo. (ANI) More Entertainment Industry News MJs     Olivia
